data.description: FINALLY, HOME ON FLINT ROAD! This charming 1400 sqft ranch-style gem, nestled on a generous 0.5-acre lot across the street from Sanford Lake, offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and serene living. Built in 2003, this lovingly cared-for abode boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and an inviting open layout. Step inside to discover a spacious living room seamlessly flowing into an open kitchen adorned with vinyl plank flooring. The primary suite is a retreat in itself, featuring a walk-in closet and a gorgeously updated master bath. Outside, enjoy the expansive backyard oasis complete with a large 16x24 barn shed, an 8x10 shed for additional storage, fire pit, and a delightful kids' play area. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to own a slice of paradise. Call today to schedule your private showing!
